    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Last updated: January 2025</p>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>YAPP collects the following information to provide our social networking services:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Profile Information:</strong> Name, profile photo, phone number</li>
        <li><strong>Location Data:</strong> Your current location to show nearby friends and spots</li>
        <li><strong>Status Updates:</strong> Your custom status messages and auto-detected statuses (driving, on call, etc.)</li>
        <li><strong>Friend Connections:</strong> Your friend list and friend requests</li>
        <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Device type, operating system, app version</li>
        <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> How you interact with the app to improve our services</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use your information to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Provide social networking features and friend connections</li>
        <li>Show your location to friends (when enabled)</li>
        <li>Display your status updates to friends</li>
        <li>Send push notifications for friend requests and updates</li>
        <li>Improve app performance and user experience</li>
        <li>Provide customer support</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Information Sharing</h2>
    <p>We share your information only with:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Your Friends:</strong> Profile information, status updates, and location (when enabled)</li>
        <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> Firebase (Google) for app functionality and data storage</li>
        <li><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> When required by law or to protect our rights</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
    <p>We use industry-standard security measures to protect your data, including encryption and secure servers provided by Firebase (Google).</p>

    <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Access your personal data</li>
        <li>Correct inaccurate information</li>
        <li>Delete your account and data</li>
        <li>Opt out of location sharing</li>
        <li>Control push notification settings</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>6. Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>YAPP is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.</p>

    <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>
    <p>Email: support@yappculture.com<br>
    Website: <a href="http://yappculture.com">yappculture.com</a></p>

    <h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.</p>
